(387, 1, '2022-05-05 07:04:20', '2022-05-05 07:04:20', '<!-- wp:html /-->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-755 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Group-115.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"539\" height=\"60\" /></p>\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"7\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<font color=black size=\"5\">\n<b>\nASIA fan joint stock company\n</b>\n</font>\n</br>\n</br>\n<font color=\"blue\" size=\"4\">\nFanning the world from Vietnam\n</font>\n</br>\n<font color=\"blue\" size=\"4\">\nASIAFAN – A 100% Group SEB-owned </br>subsidiary since 2015\n</font>\n</br>\n<p>Popular Vietnamese fan manufacturer Asia Fan was established in 1990 as an electric fan workshop Over the years demand for ASIAvina fans grew steadily resulting in the establishment of our first large-scale production facility in Vinh Loc in 2001 and a second factory line in Binh Duong in 2005.</p>\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"5\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"756\" width=\"74\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[ux_slider]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"6\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"758\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image]\n\n[ux_image id=\"760\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"761\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"759\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/ux_slider]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"9\" span__sm=\"12\" align=\"left\"]\n\n<font size=\"3\">In 2011, Asia Fan joined the renowned Groupe SEB, a worldwide housewares conglomerate based in France<br>, and became a 100% Groupe SEB-owned subsidiary in 2015.</font>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"7\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"764\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[gap height=\"40px\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"9\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<font size=\"3\">Electric specialist store chains and supermarkets. Three iconic brands have been sold in Vietnam including\n</font>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n<font size=4 color=blue><b>Vietnam - A High-priority location for R&D developmen<br>t & manufacturing of groupe SEB for South - East Asia</b></font>\n<font size=3>\nAt Groupe SEB, safety and quality are the top priorities.  Components and raw materials used are of high quality standard – only original plastic resins are used (not recycled plastic); copper cord for motor of fans instead of aluminium cord that increases the durability of the fans.\n\nIn 2013, with the support of R&D department of Groupe SEB, ASIAvina introduced electrical fans saving energy up to 25% rather than other analogous fans on the market. ASIAvina fan have achieved REACH and RoHs benchmark – the qualified standards to get allowance to export fans to extremely rigorous nations in Europe, Asia and South America.\n\nBesides manufacturing fans,  AsiaFan manufactures and supplies housewares and other small appliances directly to a wide distribution network of  general trade retailers, electric specialist store chains and supermarkets. Three iconic brands have been sold in Vietnam including:\n</font>\n[gap height=\"14px\"]\n\n<font size=3>\nEach product of ASIAvina is designed and produced with a deep understanding of our customers, ensuring that their demands of high quality performance, durability and safety are met.\n</font>\n[gap height=\"43px\"]\n\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"772\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"773\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"771\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[gap height=\"72px\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-size: x-large;\"><b> Quatlity Certificates, Awards of ASIAvina FAN</b> </span></p>\n[ux_image id=\"776\"]\n\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-780 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Group-112.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"60\" /></p>\n[row]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[row_inner]\n\n[col_inner span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"782\"]\n\n\n[/col_inner]\n[col_inner span=\"8\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[row_inner_1]\n\n[col_inner_1 span=\"5\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"783\"]\n\n\n[/col_inner_1]\n[col_inner_1 span=\"7\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_banner height=\"351px\"]\n\n[text_box width=\"100\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"50\"]\n\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> The world reference in small </span></strong></h1>\n<h1 class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">domestic equipment </span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Groupe SEB was initiated by a tinker called Antonie Lescue who<br />set up his tin workshop in 1857 in Selongey (France).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />Recent days, Groupe SEB is one of global leading corporations in</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">small domestic appliance. Groupe SEB has built a strong</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">foundation in many continents through various product lines and</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">a list of well-known brands.</p>\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n\n[/col_inner_1]\n\n[/row_inner_1]\n[ux_image id=\"785\"]\n\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-786 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Untitled-2-800x19.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"19\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-788 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Group-169-800x78.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"938\" height=\"92\" /></p>\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p align=center><span style=\"color: blue; font-size: x-large;\"> <b> The achievement of GROUPE SEB <br>through the impressive numbers </b> </span></p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"6\"]\n\n<font color=blue size=7><b>\n25\n</b>\n</font><br>\n<font size=5 color=black>\nNations\n</font><br>\nLeading brand in small<br> domestic appliances\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"6\"]\n\n<font color=blue size=7><b>\n26\n</b>\n</font><br>\n<font size=5 color=black>\nProducts\n</font><br>\nSold every second around<br> the world\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"6\"]\n\n<font color=blue size=7><b>\n200\n</b>\n</font><br>\n<font size=5 color=black>\nMillions\n</font><br>\nLorem ipsum dolor sit<br> amet, consectetur<br> adipiscing elit. Morbi vel <br>posuere velit.\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"6\"]\n\n<font color=blue size=7><b>\n25.000\n</b>\n</font><br>\n<font size=5 color=black>\nEmployees\n</font><br>\nLorem ipsum dolor sit<br> amet, consectetur<br> adipiscing elit. Morbi vel <br>posuere velit.\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<font color=blue size=7><b>\n150\n</b>\n</font><br>\n<font size=5 color=black>\nYears\n</font><br>\nLorem ipsum dolor sit<br> amet, consectetur<br> adipiscing elit. Morbi vel <br>posuere velit.\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<font color=blue size=7><b>\n29\n</b>\n</font><br>\n<font size=5 color=black>\nProduction sites\n</font><br>\nLorem ipsum dolor sit<br> amet, consectetur<br> adipiscing elit. Morbi vel <br>posuere velit.\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<font color=blue size=7><b>\n107</b>\n</font><br>\n<font size=5 color=black>\nRegistered\n</font><br>\nLorem ipsum dolor sit<br> amet, consectetur<br> adipiscing elit. Morbi vel <br>posuere velit.\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[ux_image id=\"776\"]\n\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Further information about Groupe SEB, please download the brochure\n<font color=blue>\n<u>\n<i>\nhere\n</i>\n</u>\n</font>\n</p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'About us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed